summary: Complete FDO end-to-end protocol testing
description: |
    Comprehensive FDO testing covering:
    - Certificate infrastructure setup
    - Multi-server orchestration (manufacturer, rendezvous, owner)
    - Device initialization and onboarding
    - ServiceInfo module testing
    - Protocol validation

test: ../../rpm/test-onboarding.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

require:
  - go-fdo-server
  - go-fdo-server-manufacturer
  - go-fdo-server-owner
  - go-fdo-server-rendezvous

tag:
  - fdo
  - e2e
  - protocol
  - onboarding
  - rpm
  - server
